WEBVTT

00:00:02.836 --> 00:00:03.871
NARRATOR: The rebuilding
of Lumiose City continues,

00:00:04.872 --> 00:00:06.840
and at the same time,

00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:09.142
our heroes are thinking
about what their futures hold...

00:00:09.142 --> 00:00:10.477
and of course,
that includes Serena.

00:00:21.722 --> 00:00:24.358
PALERMO: All right.

00:00:24.358 --> 00:00:26.793
PALERMO: Keep on your
journey to your heart's content.

00:00:26.793 --> 00:00:28.896
And once you're all
ready for the next step,

00:00:28.896 --> 00:00:30.364
you just give me a call.

00:00:34.968 --> 00:00:36.236
BONNIE: Hey, look at that!

00:00:38.038 --> 00:00:39.640
ANNOUNCER: The light of hope
even illuminated Prism Tower!

00:00:42.342 --> 00:00:44.578
ANNOUNCER: There are
still many wounds to be healed

00:00:44.578 --> 00:00:46.947
in Lumiose City, but I'm
sure this light will guide us

00:00:46.947 --> 00:00:49.416
as we continue our recovery!

00:00:49.416 --> 00:00:51.985
BONNIE: You know, lighting up
Prism Tower was great!

00:00:51.985 --> 00:00:54.721
Everybody loved it.
All those smiles!

00:00:54.721 --> 00:00:56.823
DEDENNE: [AGREEMENT]

00:00:56.823 --> 00:00:58.425
CLEMONT: It was great.

00:00:58.425 --> 00:00:59.693
One of our first
big steps to recovery.

00:01:07.434 --> 00:01:08.702
SYCAMORE: Oh, I see.

00:01:08.702 --> 00:01:09.202
SERENA: What do you think?

00:01:10.938 --> 00:01:12.472
SYCAMORE:
I think it's a great idea!

00:01:12.472 --> 00:01:14.942
Okay. I'll be glad to help out.

00:01:14.942 --> 00:01:17.344
SERENA: Thank you so much!

00:01:17.344 --> 00:01:18.845
PANCHAM: [EXCITED]
BRAIXEN, SYLVEON: [EXCITED]

00:01:25.152 --> 00:01:27.588
I stand tall
'Cause I know I'm a winner

